Titolo: Juiced 2: Hot Import Nights

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Juiced 2: Hot Import Nights is a racing video game developed by Juice Games for various platforms. The PlayStation 2, Xbox 360 and Nintendo DS versions were released in September 2007, while PlayStation Portable and PlayStation 3 versions were released in October; Microsoft Windows version was released in November. It is a sequel to the 2005 game Juiced. It was developed by Juice Games and published by THQ. The game utilizes more advanced car modification methods in comparison to its predecessor.
Ursula Mayes is on the cover of the game on all platforms.
A Wii version was planned but was cancelled.

Genere: Racing 

Valutazione: 68
